caption: We like a lot to go out. Last night we  found this fine place which we didn’t know before. We passed a beautiful time there with exceptional cooking and a courteous stuff and  a professional  chef. We  added this restaurant in our phone list  and we shall no doubt return very soon. We warmly recommend.
Best spot to have something when in a rush. Their customer service is fast, pricing is fair, excellent ambience. I highly recommend this spot.
A favorite spot for Cheap food. I'll return with my friends. Feeling here is like a restaurant in Fort Worth I liked.
cheap food and the atmosphere at this location is great. The food was so savory. I look forward to a return visit. The place has a good atmosphere.
My preferred place for quality cheap food. Loved this place from the first taste.
Great location for tasty Cheap food. Good place to relax and unwind.  Looking forward to a return trip. This place has a good atmosphere.
delicious food offered but I need more variety of food for more choices
Great service and great food. Currently closed due to COVID.

I have been frequenting SRO for 15 years now.   The soups are excellent and the burger are delicious.   In the winter months the chili is a must try.   Feeling like something a little less fast food like?  Try the fitness plate.   Many of the employees have been here since they opened in the early 90s.  Says something about the people who run it.
Great burgers. Quick walk from the loop. Worth it!

Yummy hamburger with a pretzel bun. The gyro plate was decent. The fitness plate was also perfect for my wife. We were in a hurry and needed decent food fast. We got exactly that! I also really appreciated all the pictures and autographed jerseys on the wall. It brought back a lot of cool memories.
The burger filled not only my stomach, but also my soul.
Awesome gyros!
Good quick local bite. I like the Cajun Chicken and the burgers. Fries are always cooked perfectly
I tried this spot once with my friend and I am hooked ever since. I loved the fantastic ambience and fresh food and drinks. 5 stars.
This place obviously knows how to serve their customers. Regularly with a super nice attitude. The food is conveniently priced, regularly flavorful and neat.
The food is always fresh and delicious, workers gives good service. I really like how clean it is and vibes. Keep up the good work.
Always quick and tasty!
I always get their gyros, I love them. Nice friendly establishment
amazing food amazing setting just an overall fantastic experience, must try the cheddar fries
Classic American food restaurant
Sometimes out of the food we would like to buy even though we come an hour after opening. Friendly staff and delicious food
Burgers were delicious and very filling.  We split fries and it was too much food.  Prices were very reasonable and service was friendly and quick.  Full of great Chicago sports memorabilia.
This place knows how to treat their clients. Always with a super nice approach. The food is fairly priced, regularly delicious and neat.
Grilled sro chicken not too bad, but for $9 a bit of fries would have been good. The chicken fingers remind wife of Dino Nuggets. Service was great though

Standing Room Only is a good place for sandwiches in the Printers Row area of Chicago. They have a different fresh soup every day, seasonal chili, and great sandwiches. I like their hot dogs, Cajun Chicken sandwich, and the "Boss" burger which is served with pepperjack cheese on a pretzel roll. Excellent lunch stop in Printers Row. Good selection of burgers and other sandwiches. Fries are excellent. Has outdoor seating if you desire that. Great place
Love the spicy black bean burger.

I though Standing Room Only would be crowded and have a Broadway theater theme. Wrong and wrong. Above our table was a cool photo of the Chicago Bears at the 1985 Super Bowl . On the wall across us was memorabilia from the Chicago Cubs, the reigning World Series champions. And SRO was not overly crowded--about two-third full, with lots of businessmen, only 3 blocks from the financial district. My son had a big cheeseburger and I had a grilled chicken sandwich. Good fries. Highly recommend for sports fans and families, even if you're not from Chicago, for the memories plastered on walls.
I've been there twice, tried something different each time and was impressed each time. And the 20% military discount was very much appreciated.
Good food . Healthy options
Overpriced for the quality of food
Nice fries
Was okay food but to expensive and the bun to my burger was way to small had to to eat with a fork
Ordered and ran to train, then found I paid $9 for a 6" sub swimming in dressing and stingy amount of Turkey. Waste of money.

A great joint to be rescued from chain burgers.A place to enjoy turkey burgers,gyros hot dogs and more.Great sports memorabilia. Service good .Quality good.Pricey but so worth it.Decor commercial.Difficult and expensive street parking. AWARDED 2 YUMS ON A SCALE OF 3
Thea best cheese fries and turkey burgers 🍔
Local place with all the options for a perfect burger and fries...for anyone...seriously
The Cajun chicken sandwich is the best

Amazing chicken sandwich, sweet potato fries, and their burgers aren't bad either. Haven't tried much but what I have it's really, really good. And don't be fooled by the name, they actually have a lot of seating. It's a fair sized restaurant with a lot of sports memorabilia.
Willis gives it Thumbs Up.
Uh. The turkey chilli! No. Wait. Get a Rookie sandwich.
Great turkey burgers
Good prices, sports diner atmosphere, and really good food. The grilled chicken taste very fresh and they have good healthy options.
EXCELLENT FOOD GOOD PRICE NICE PORTIONS

Best turkey chili anywhere!
Turkey chili is fantastic.
Really predictable American Grill
The Cajun chicken sandwich is on point! Found my new go to lunch spot!
Great turkey burgers and friendly service
Good food and friendly service and staff. Reliable and convenient.

You know you love a place when you haven't had it in awhile but you're up at 1230 a.m. thinking about it! Been going here on and off for over 20 years. Great food, not expensive at all. Real friendly staff. Wide variety on the menu.Cool place and nice atmosphere in Printers Row. Can't wait to go back again!
This place always has great food.  Great spot, a little off the beaten path but worth the walk.  Great food and great service.
Get the BOSS burger!
Overall I like this place. Good ambiance. Food is reliably good! Gyros and chicken sandwiches are my go to. Always tasty. Definitely recommend.
Grilled cheese was amazing, fries were alright. Very sports themed casual place
Great food!!!

Awesome food! Burger, chicken strips, and cheesy fries were a hit with the kids but my fav was the cajun chicken fitness platter--great flavor and came with huge grilled pepper pieces, sliced carrots, mushroom and rice. Hard to find healthy and delicious fast food, so I was impressed. Decor is fun vibe with nostalgic sports memorabilia. Appreciate they discount 20% for military, police and fire.
Good service, good food, and not expensive
Good burger here.
Best Chilly ive tasted nice kick, gyros are good and so is the hot dog.
Great fast food especially Gyros.  Generous servings.
Amazing turkey burger and great atmosphere
Excellent place for a quick lunch.
Always good
I went here for a short while after school, the place itself is very nice as well as the food. I would recommend this place for a quick affordable place to eat.

Ordered the turkey burger w everything... And a cup for water. Price came out to be about 10.00 dollars.  I paid and sat down..   took a bit of time to make... ding ding. Picked up the burger... No fries.  Didn't expect fries.... But when I heard the price I don't know it kinda felt like fries would be included ... And the whole reason I ventured in was because it was getting cold and I saw a sign that said TURKEY Burger...  Over all it was a fresh ice berg lettuce and tomato slice with a nice turkey burger etc.. took about five bites and it was gone. Mmmm....oh it's on a toasty bun. I should have checked the menu for better deals but I was hungry.
Cheese fries!
I get lunch from here all the time! The Greek salad dressing is probably one of my favorite dressings ever
Good burgers, good fries.  They used to be expensive and we stopped going.  Now that everyone else has caught up...
I like the place here. Small but has a good atmosphere.. The costumer service was great. Friendly staffs..
Great burgers! Cheap, fast, and delicious! Fun atmosphere too! Lots of sports memorabilia.
Great turkey burgers and grilled veggies.
Their black bean burger is right up there with best veggie burger I've ever had. The sweet potato fries are sublime.
Great corned beef and pastrami sandwiches. Nice quick and clean location. You can always find a park if you're driving.
Fun spot, family run place that's been here for years. Sports fans will love it, lots of sports memorabilia.
Good stuff
Pricey but always tasty.
Love there food 😉
Great service need to expand the menu cajun chicken sandwich the best
Try the SRO Chicken Sandwich
Only get the special of the day, it's the best value. Contrary to the name, there is plenty of seating. Also, get a punch card to save.

Seriously one of the best places to eat in Chicago, no doubt. Very friendly staff, very chill vibe inside (very sport-related) and AMAZING food. I always get the Chicago-Style w/ fries and a drink every time I go and it's perfect every single time, all for only about $8.80.  I've been here at least 2 dozen times already and feel guilty for not writing an amazing review yet!
Excellent Philly Cheese Steak sandwich!
Cool spot for the best Turkey burger, cheeseburger in chicago!! Try the sweet pattie fries!!♡♡
Go there a few times per month.  But a burger, fries and a coke will run you over $13.  No tipping and you get a ton of crinkle fries, but still, $13 for lunch gets expensive quickly.
Classic fast food.  Delicious.  Consistent.   A neighborhood staple
I have been coming here for 13+ years. Food is always tasty and the fries are always served hot! Their cheese fries are the bomb!

I love this place so much. The food is perfect and delicious every time. If you want high quality sandwiches, chicken tenders, delicious fries, and great dogs this is the place to go! The service is fast, the tables are clean, and there's usually always a table!
Anything is good but love sro burger
They have a bank's hours, and the service is brusque at best. Maybe that's their schtick. I don't care for it.
